        <item>
            <title>Version 1.2 for Leopard</title>
						<sparkle:releaseNotesLink>
							http://pornel.net/imageoptim/en/
						</sparkle:releaseNotesLink>
            <pubDate>Sat, 29 Nov 2008 19:19:25 +0000</pubDate>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>10.5.7</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[
            <p>ImageOptim now requires Leopard (10.5.7).</p>
            <ul>
                <li>New: Faster and more stable thanks to new Leopard APIs.</li>
                <li>New: Can handle order of magnitude more files at once.</li>
                <li>New: Avoids writing many files to disk at the same time.</li>
                <li>New: Checks actual file type rather than rely on filename extension.</li>
                <li>Fix: Temporary files are cleaned up on exit.</li>
                <li>Fix: Errors during optimisations don't slow down or lock up ImageOptim.</li>
            </ul>
            ]]></description>
